{
  "id": "59c35ec60b80800012202cfa",
  "title": "クロスエントロピー",
  "created": 1505976010,
  "updated": 1509159548,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "59c35ec60b80800012202cfa",
      "text": "クロスエントロピー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976010,
      "updated": 1505976010
    },
    {
      "id": "59c35ec9aff09e00005bc2e0",
      "text": "\tp, qが離散的な確率分布であるときのクロスエントロピー:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976010,
      "updated": 1505977782
    },
    {
      "id": "59c35f2aaff09e00005bc2e1",
      "text": " [$ H(p,q) = -\\sum_x p(x) \\log q(x)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976107,
      "updated": 1505976212
    },
    {
      "id": "59c365b6aff09e00005bc2f1",
      "text": "  xは多クラス分類の文脈ならクラスに相当する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505977783,
      "updated": 1505977804
    },
    {
      "id": "59c35f3daff09e00005bc2e2",
      "text": " xが{0, 1}である時:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976126,
      "updated": 1505976185
    },
    {
      "id": "59c35f60aff09e00005bc2e3",
      "text": " [$ H(p, q) = -\\{ p(0)\\log q(0) + p(1)\\log q(1) \\}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976162,
      "updated": 1505976249
    },
    {
      "id": "59c35fb8aff09e00005bc2e4",
      "text": " 0である確率と1である確率を足せば1なので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976250,
      "updated": 1505976303
    },
    {
      "id": "59c35fefaff09e00005bc2e5",
      "text": " [$ H(p, q) = -\\{ (1 - p(1))\\log (1 - q(1)) + p(1)\\log q(1) \\}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976305,
      "updated": 1505976381
    },
    {
      "id": "59c3603daff09e00005bc2e6",
      "text": " pが1である確率をt、qが1である確率をyとして書きなおすと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976383,
      "updated": 1505978906
    },
    {
      "id": "59c3606aaff09e00005bc2e8",
      "text": " [$ H(p, q) = -\\{ (1 - t)\\log (1 - y) + t \\log y \\}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505976427,
      "updated": 1505978913
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36887aff09e00005bc2f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505978505,
      "updated": 1505978898
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36888aff09e00005bc2f5",
      "text": "[* クロスエントロピーとLog lossに関する混乱の多くは、sumが何についてのものかをあいまいにすることが原因]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505978505,
      "updated": 1509159502
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36eb6aff09e00005bc2f9",
      "text": "\t上記のとおり、xがクラスを走る前提で、2クラス分類なら下記が成り立つ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505980087,
      "updated": 1505980448
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36ee9aff09e00005bc2fa",
      "text": " [$ -\\sum_x p(x) \\log q(x) = -\\{ (1 - t)\\log (1 - y) + t \\log y \\}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505980138,
      "updated": 1505980201
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36eebaff09e00005bc2fb",
      "text": " iが各データを走る前提で全データの損失の和を計算するなら下記が成り立つ。(上式をsum_iでくるんだだけ)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505980140,
      "updated": 1505980464
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36f0aaff09e00005bc2fc",
      "text": " [$ -\\sum_i \\sum_x p(x) \\log q(x) = -\\sum_i \\{ (1 - t)\\log (1 - y) + t \\log y \\}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505980171,
      "updated": 1505980223
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36f3faff09e00005bc2fe",
      "text": " この2つを混同して下記2つを並べて比較したりするのは無意味",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505980225,
      "updated": 1505980371
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36f2faff09e00005bc2fd",
      "text": " [$ -\\sum_x p(x) \\log q(x) ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505980208,
      "updated": 1505980312
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36f96aff09e00005bc2ff",
      "text": " [$ -\\sum_i \\{t \\log y + (1 - t)\\log (1 - y)\\}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505980312,
      "updated": 1505980349
    },
    {
      "id": "59c36fa9aff09e00005bc300",
      "text": "\t「クロスエントロピーとLog lossは同じ！」という表現で上2つの式を同一視したりすると破滅する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1505980331,
      "updated": 1509159548
    }
  ]
}